high_descs: Turn around and go to the bathroom sink.
Open the cabinet under the left sink and take out the dirty rag.
Move towards the right of the sink.
Wash the towel in the left sink under running water and take it out.
Turn left and go to the right side of the toilet.
Place the rag on the top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed rag on the top of the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn around and locate the sink.
Open the cabinet below the sink and pick up the cloth.
Hold the cloth and look around.
Place the cloth in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the cloth.
Carry the cloth and take a step to the left.
Place the cloth on the tank of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a cloth and put it on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the left sink on the vanity.
Open the left cabinet under the sink, pick up the dirty towel inside and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the middle of the two sinks on the vanity.
Put the dirty towel inside the left sink, rinse it off and pick it back up.
Turn around, take a right and walk to the counter next to the white toilet.
Put the clean towel on the right side of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean towel on a toilet tank.
